data.meta_description: ++ BANDUNGMOVIES LIST UPDATEEE - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document lists prices for hard disk filling services in Bandung, Indonesia. It provides prices for filling various sized hard disks with movies in different formats, including standard definition movies priced at Rp10,000 each, and 3D movies priced at Rp15,000 each. Delivery using Gojek motorcycle taxis is available for a fee. The minimum order is to fill the hard disk.
